---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="EXPRESS BOOKS™ | Publish a Short Christian Book in 90 Days"
	description="EXPRESS BOOKS™ by Spirit Media — compact, high-impact Christian books read in one sitting. Share your message fast. Publish in as few as 90 days. Paperback, eBook & PDF."
	ogImage="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/pmowd8uo/production/91eff73d0166bac824bdf85f24744ce93fe49895-1536x1024.png"
>
	<Fragment slot="head">
		<meta name="keywords" content="Christian book publishing, short Christian book, publish in 90 days, EXPRESS BOOKS, Spirit Media Publishing, self publish Christian book, Christian author, compact book publishing, ministry book, faith book publishing" />
		<meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
		<meta property="og:site_name" content="Spirit Media Publishing" />
		<meta property="og:locale" content="en_US" />
		<script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org",
			"@type": "Service",
			"name": "EXPRESS BOOKS™",
			"description": "A compact Christian book publishing program by Spirit Media — publish a high-impact book in 90 days or less in paperback, eBook, and PDF formats.",
			"provider": {
				"@type": "Organization",
				"name": "Spirit Media Publishing",
				"url": "https://spiritmediapublishing.com"
			},
			"url": "https://spiritmediapublishing.com/express-books",
			"image": "https://spiritmediapublishing.com/express-books.png",
			"serviceType": "Christian Book Publishing",
			"areaServed": "Worldwide"
		})}</script>
	</Fragment>
	<main id="main-content">

		<!-- HERO -->
		<section class="bg-stone-50 px-6 py-12 lg:py-16 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
					<div class="hero-stagger">
						<p class="eyebrow eyebrow-red mb-4">EXPRESS BOOKS™</p>
						<h1 class="type-hero">Fast reads.<br /><span class="text-red">Lasting impact.</span></h1>
						<p class="mt-6 type-body-lg max-w-xl">Not every message needs 300 pages. Some of the most powerful truths can be shared in under an hour.</p>
						<div class="mt-8">
							<a href="/contact" class="rounded-md bg-red px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-red-deep">Request a Call →</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="hidden lg:flex items-center justify-center" data-animate="zoom-in">
						<img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/pmowd8uo/production/91eff73d0166bac824bdf85f24744ce93fe49895-1536x1024.png" alt="EXPRESS BOOKS™ — Fast reads, lasting impact" class="w-full rounded-2xl" />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ABOUT -->
		<section class="bg-stone-100 py-12 lg:py-20 px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<p class="eyebrow eyebrow-red mb-3" data-animate="fade-up">The Format</p>
				<h2 class="type-section-heading mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">Publishing Designed for Multiplication</h2>
				<p class="type-body-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">EXPRESS BOOKS™ is Spirit Media's signature publishing format — intentionally compact books designed to be read in a single sitting. No filler. No fluff. Just your message, distilled to its most potent form. Transformation that lasts a lifetime.</p>
				<p class="type-body-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="3">At roughly 80 pages, every EXPRESS BOOK™ is affordably priced for easy sharing — hand one to a friend, leave one in a waiting room, ship a box to a pastor overseas. This is publishing designed for multiplication.</p>
				<p class="type-body-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="4">Every EXPRESS BOOK™ is published in three formats: paperback, eBook, and downloadable PDF — with global distribution through Amazon, IngramSpark, and eBook stores worldwide.</p>
				<img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/pmowd8uo/production/7c80cdd49ffff8d9682d801d96362621e052ed0e-3300x476.png" alt="EXPRESS BOOKS™" class="w-full mt-10 rounded-2xl" data-animate="fade-up" />
				<p class="type-body-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed mt-6" data-animate="fade-up">Join the new and elite category of EXPRESS BOOK™.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- 90-DAY PROCESS -->
		<section class="bg-stone-600 px-6 py-10 lg:py-16 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
				<div class="text-center mb-12">
					<p class="eyebrow eyebrow-red mb-3" data-animate="fade-up">The Process</p>
					<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">From Idea to Published in 90 Days</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
					{[
						{ step: '01', title: 'Message Clarity', body: 'We help you identify your core message and define your reader — distilling years of experience into one focused book of 12,000–15,000 words.' },
						{ step: '02', title: 'Write & Edit', body: 'You write and we edit — or our Angel Writers can write it for you, in your own words, in as little as one month.' },
						{ step: '03', title: 'Design & Format', body: 'Professional cover design and interior layout — print-ready for paperback and formatted for eBook and PDF.' },
						{ step: '04', title: 'Publish & Distribute', body: 'Global launch through Amazon, IngramSpark, and eBook stores worldwide. Your book in readers\' hands fast.' },
					].map(({ step, title, body }, i) => (
						<div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay={String(i + 1)}>
							<p class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-red mb-3">{step}</p>
							<h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">{title}</h3>
							<p class="text-stone-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">{body}</p>
						</div>
					))}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- FORMATS -->
		<section class="bg-stone-50 py-12 lg:py-20 px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/pmowd8uo/production/7833f28378750a49205269eb39a6c2c19f31b92d-1058x394.png" alt="EXPRESS BOOKS Collection" class="w-1/2 mx-auto rounded-2xl mb-8" data-animate="fade-up" />
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<div class="bg-stone-100 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-stone-200 text-center" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">
						<div class="flex h-14 w-14 mx-auto items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-wash text-red mb-4">
							<svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 0 0 6 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 1 6 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 0 1 6-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 0 18 18a8.967 8.967 0 0 0-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25" /></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="type-card-heading mb-2">Paperback</h3>
						<p class="type-body-sm text-stone-600">Roughly 80 pages, affordably priced for easy sharing and multiplication.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-stone-100 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-stone-200 text-center" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">
						<div class="flex h-14 w-14 mx-auto items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-wash text-red mb-4">
							<svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 1.5H8.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 6 3.75v16.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25h7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18 20.25V3.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H13.5m-3 0V3h3V1.5m-3 0h3m-6 18.75h6" /></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="type-card-heading mb-2">eBook</h3>
						<p class="type-body-sm text-stone-600">Digital distribution to 1 billion eBook users worldwide.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-stone-100 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-stone-200 text-center" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="3">
						<div class="flex h-14 w-14 mx-auto items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-wash text-red mb-4">
							<svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m2.25 0H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z" /></svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="type-card-heading mb-2">Downloadable PDF</h3>
						<p class="type-body-sm text-stone-600">Accessible anywhere, on any device. Perfect for global distribution.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA -->
		<!-- EXTRACTING -->
		<section class="bg-stone-100 py-12 lg:py-20 px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<p class="eyebrow eyebrow-red mb-3" data-animate="fade-up">Extracting</p>
				<h2 class="type-section-heading mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">Most Books Already Contain EXPRESS BOOKS™</h2>
				<p class="type-body-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">If you've already published a book of 30,000–50,000 words, there's a good chance one or more EXPRESS BOOKS™ are waiting inside it. Give our team your existing manuscript and we'll identify the 12,000–15,000 word sections with the focus and power to stand alone as their own EXPRESS BOOK™.</p>
				<p class="type-body-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="3">This is one of the most effective ways to revitalize existing content. Your readers will welcome a sharpened, focused EXPRESS BOOK™ drawn from a work they already love — and new readers will discover your greater work through it. It's a win-win for every book you've ever published.</p>
				<p class="type-body-lg text-stone-700 leading-relaxed mb-8" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="4">It's a win-win for every book you've ever published.</p>
				<a href="/contact" class="rounded-md bg-red px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-red-deep" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="5">Request a Free Proposal →</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA -->
		<section class="bg-red px-6 py-12 lg:py-20 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl mb-4" data-animate="fade-up">Ready to publish your EXPRESS BOOK™?</h2>
				<p class="text-stone-200 type-body-lg mb-8" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">Your message doesn't need 300 pages. Let us help you distill it to its most powerful form.</p>
				<a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-stone-50 text-red font-semibold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-md hover:bg-red-wash transition-colors" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">Request a Call →</a>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
